==Introduction==
陸軍で開発、運用されていたオートジャイロ。その対潜戦闘力を強化したif強化型改修機です。<br>
現代の艦載ヘリコプターの先祖ともいえる、回転翼の艦載対潜哨戒機、全通甲板を持つ強襲揚陸艦や軽空母、改装航空戦艦、航空甲板を持つ航空巡洋艦などで運用可能です。

''This is an autogyro that was developed and operated by the Army. It is a modified version with enhanced anti-submarine capabilities.''<br>
''It is the ancestor of the modern shipborne helicopter, as a rotary-wing anti-submarine patrol aircraft, and can be operated from landing ships with flight decks, light aircraft carriers, aviation battleships, and aviation cruisers.''

